title: Doughboys Double 14 - Unsatisfied Yelpers with Erin Whitehead

description:
Free preview of Doughboys Double!

Erin Whitehead of Wild Horses returns to the podcast as we present a biggie size edition of our much requested Doughboys 1.0 segment An Unsatisfied Yelper. But first, Mitch challenges Erin and Wiger to a Dr Pepper guessing game.

To subscribe to the Doughboys Double go to: patreon.com/doughboys
